metadata.name: ENTER THE DARKROOM
metadata.description:
View through a peephole exposing deep tones of reds, leaving us with a sultry and mysterious feeling through a spectator view




Collection ‘Meet Me In My Dream’ is a visual interpretation of dream states depicting personal memories and fantasies in monochromatic tones. Each piece is an exploration of sensuality and expression of female form - with intention to inspire viewers to open their imagination and subconsciously dive in to their own sexual and love fantasies.

VR SHOW: http://bit.ly/3Bf9oHr
